zipkin-cpp-opentracing
------------------------------------------
OpenTracing Tracer implementation for Zipkin in C++

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.0.7-1
  libcurl4-7.65.0-1
  libgcc1-7.4.0-1
  libopentracing1-1.5.1-1bl1
  libstdc++6-7.4.0-1
  libzipkin0-0.5.2-1bl1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.29-1
  cmake-3.13.1-1
  cygport-0.33.1-1
  gcc-core-7.4.0-1
  gcc-g++-7.4.0-1
  ninja-1.9.0-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/rnburn/zipkin-cpp-opentracing

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/rnburn/zipkin-cpp-opentracing/archive/v0.5.2.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack zipkin-cpp-opentracing-0.5.2-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./zipkin-cpp-opentracing-0.5.2-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/zipkin-cpp-opentracing-0.5.2-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/zipkin-cpp-opentracing-0.5.2-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libzipkin0-0.5.2-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libzipkin-devel-0.5.2-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(zipkin-cpp-opentracing)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/zipkin-cpp-opentracing.README
  /usr/share/doc/zipkin-cpp-opentracing/LICENSE
  /usr/share/doc/zipkin-cpp-opentracing/README.md

(libzipkin0)
  /usr/bin/cygzipkin-0.dll
  /usr/bin/cygzipkin_opentracing-0.dll

(libzipkin-devel)
  /usr/include/zipkin/flags.h
  /usr/include/zipkin/hex.h
  /usr/include/zipkin/ip_address.h
  /usr/include/zipkin/opentracing.h
  /usr/include/zipkin/optional.h
  /usr/include/zipkin/span_context.h
  /usr/include/zipkin/trace_id.h
  /usr/include/zipkin/tracer.h
  /usr/include/zipkin/tracer_interface.h
  /usr/include/zipkin/utility.h
  /usr/include/zipkin/zipkin_core_types.h
  /usr/lib/libzipkin.dll.a
  /usr/lib/libzipkin_opentracing.dll.a

